<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="well">

      <a class="twitter-timeline" data-dnt="true" href="https://twitter.com/AthensMinecraft" data-widget-id="471126696138002432">Tweets by @AthensMinecraft</a>
              <script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js"></script>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="well">
      <h2>FAQ</h2>
      <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne">
                How do I get Whitelisted?
              </a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
            <div class="panel-body">
              Currently you will need to fill out an application on this thread. We may also request an example of a recent build, at our discretion. Whitelists are shared between all servers, so our members will get access to our Vanilla and modded servers.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo">
                Do I have to subscribe to play/pay any money?
              </a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
              We do have an option for supporters to assist with server costs, which is available here. All money used for subscribers is used for this purpose, and there are no in-game perks associated. You do not need to pay to be whitelisted however, and paid members are subject to the same rules as our regular members. Supporters will receive access to supporter-only events about every month, including UHC games, CTM maps, etc.

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThree">
                Can I purchase any in-game items to help me get started?
              </a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                No, we are a vanilla survival server and regardless of your subscription rank we do not give any in-game perks. We feel this is the best way to level the playing field for those who cannot subscribe to support us.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div> <!-- End FAQ -->
